subject: Swimming
Olympic Games (2012)
Olympic Games
lead_paragraph: Dana Vollmer was a surprise Olympian for the United States in 2004, but a washout in 2008. At this year’s Olympic swimming trials, she set an American record in the 100 butterfly.
